{# Welcome :wave:. The content of this page is automatically generated based on Curio's CLI help files. #}

{% set items = [curio_scan, curio_init] %}
<h1>Commands</h1>

<p>Curio offers a number of commands to use and customize the CLI to your needs.</p>
<ul>
  {% for item in items %}
    <li>
      <a href="#{{ item.name | trim}}">{{ item.name | trim}}</a>: {{item.synopsis}}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

{% for item in items %}
  <h2 class="inline-block bg-main-100 p-1 rounded-md leading-none font-mono" id="{{ item.name | trim | e}}">curio {{ item.name | trim | escape }}</h2>

  <p>{{item.synopsis}}</p>

  <pre><code class="lang-bash">curio {{item.usage | trim}}</code></pre>

  <h3 id="{{item.name | trim}}-flags">Flags</h3>
  <table class="table-auto">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Description</th>
        <th>Default Value</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for option in item.options -%}
        <tr>
          <td>
            {% if option.shorthand %}
              <code class="">-{{option.shorthand}}</code>, {% endif %}
            <code class="">--{{option.name}}</code>
          </td>
          <td>{{option.usage}}</td>
          <td>{{option.default_value}}</td>
        </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  {% if item.example %}
    <h3 id="{{item.name | trim}}-usage">Usage</h3>
    <pre><code class="lang-bash">{{item.example}}</code></pre>
  {% endif %}
  {% if item.aliases %}
    <h3 id="{{item.name | trim}}-aliases">Aliases</h3>
    <p>In addition to the primary <code>{{ item.name | trim }}</code> command, you can also use <code>{{ item.aliases | trim}}</code> in place of it.
    </p>
  {% endif %}

{% endfor %}

<h2 id="global-flags">Global flags</h2>
<p>Use these flags to get more information about the <code class="inline-block bg-main-100 p-1 rounded-md leading-none font-mono m-0">curio</code> CLI.</p>
<h3 class="inline-block bg-main-100 p-1 rounded-md leading-none font-mono m-0" id="flags-version">--version</h3>
<p>Prints the installed Curio version number.</p>
<h3 class="inline-block bg-main-100 p-1 rounded-md leading-none font-mono m-0" id="flags-version">--help</h3>
<p>Prints the in-app help information for Curio.</p>